<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>483</hymn_number>
<key>D</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Sunparnak ram tha a um, Vawlei nunnak pinlei ah, Khua-ruahhar tlanhnak
 tuanbia cu an hla dawh bik in an hloi.

[C1]
   Donglo dawtnak le upatnak, (le u patnak) ruah khawh lo sunparnak cu
   (sunparnak), tlanhnak kong (A tlanhnak kong) donglo lawmhnak cu (lo
   lawmhnak cu), tlanh ciami hna hla a si (hna hla a si.)

[V2]
 Lawmhnak hla hodah a sa lai, Zungzal hmunmi caan chungah,
 Ngaih-chiatnak a um ti lai lo, Mitthli vialte a hul lai.

[C2]
   Donglo dawtnak le upatnak, (le u patnak) ruah khawh lo sunparnak cu
   (sunparnak), tlanhnak kong (A tlanhnak kong) donglo lawmhnak cu (lo
   lawmhnak cu), tlanh ciami hna hla a si (hna hla a si.)

[V3]
 Pathian tlanhnak tuanbia hla dawh, Zungzal hodah a sa lai, Tihnung
 harnak in a luatmi, Sual teitu nih an sak lai.

[C3]
   Donglo dawtnak le upatnak, (le u patnak) ruah khawh lo sunparnak cu
   (sunparnak), tlanhnak kong (A tlanhnak kong) donglo lawmhnak cu (lo
   lawmhnak cu), tlanh ciami hna hla a si (hna hla a si.)</lyrics>
<title>TLANH CIAMI HNA HLA CH483</title>
</song>